word:
Servants of the Wicked One--He who drinks in the spirit of Christ will let it flow forth in kind words, and be expressed in courteous deportment. . . . But those who profess the truth and at the same time are rough, and sour, and unkind in words and deportment, have not learned of Jesus; 
                                                                           143
all these manifestations show that they are yet servants of the wicked one.--OHC 238.
